data.text:
Overnight stop in Carnarvon – stayed at the Big 4 after doing some shopping.

Lots of fresh produce and a few sights nearby, blowholes is about 70k’s north and wroth a visit. There’s a few touristy things around town too.

Spent midday at the blow holes. Quite fun!

Cooked up some lunch in the oven while taking pics of the huge waves crashing against the coast.

Crazy kids jumping down on the rocks almost getting washed away.

Drove south a few hundred k’s and camped on the side of the highway.
